		class=&#34;gallery-image&#34; 
		data-flex-grow=&#34;223&#34;
		data-flex-basis=&#34;536px&#34;
	
&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;ul&gt;
&lt;li&gt;结束后记得卸载（即弹出ISO文件）&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;/ul&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;img src=&#34;https://scau-jiwei.gitee.io/p/office-tool-plus-%E4%BD%BF%E7%94%A8%E6%95%99%E7%A8%8B/2_018.png&#34;
